===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 26 people, 12 households, and 9 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A14880&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A14880&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 90.3 inhabitants per square mile (34.9/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 12 housing units at an average density of 41.7 per square mile (16.1/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/> All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A14880&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 12 households, 25.0% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 33.3% were [[Marriage|married-couple households]], 25.0% were cohabitating couples, 25.0% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present, and 16.7% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. 25.0% of households were non-families. 25.0% of households were made up of individuals, and 16.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years old or older. There were 12 housing units, of which 0.0% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age in the city was 39.5 years. 15.4% of residents were under the age of 18 and 15.4% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females there were 116.7 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 144.4 males age 18 and over. The age distribution was 15.4% under the age of 20, 3.8% from 20 to 24, 42.3% from 25 to 44, 23.1% from 45 to 64, and 15.4% 65 or older. The gender makeup of the city was 53.8% male and 46.2% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

